text: Azteca 7 (also called: El Siete) is a Mexican television network, owned by TV Azteca, is found both via cable and satellite. This television network is in historical competition with the Televisa channel: Canal 5. == Other websites == * Azteca 7 website * TV Azteca website Category:Television networks Category:Mexican culture Category:1985 establishments in North America
